This paper deals with the creation and sharing of online memes, which involves social interactions and communication among individuals. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.SI (Social and Information Networks). The paper also involves statistical modeling and simulation, which could fall under cs.SD (Software Engineering) or cs.CY (Computational Geometry). Additionally, the paper discusses the behavior of individuals and their decision-making processes, which could be relevant to cs.SOC (Social and Economic Networks) or cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction).
